{"tid":1155761,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有留意呢隻mmorpg,Mad world?","createTime":"2019-05-15T07:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T03:41:48.000Z","uid":48791,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"797e8ffc9d029ff218c80bfdd016cb8222ca9789","tid":1155761,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"內容全抄巴哈<br />\n<br />\n&quot;《Mad World》採用開發團隊自製的引擎「Jandi Engine」進行製作，號稱不僅能呈現生動的 2D 戰鬥畫面外，也可實現更順暢的 PVP 對戰體驗，遊戲結合手繪 2D 藝術風格，且遊戲沒有「職業」這樣的設定，玩家可以透過升級獲得的點數自由強化角色的素質能力。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7Nq3if.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7Nq3if.jpg&h=c1795a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSbWqwB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSbWqwB.jpg&h=2b98ec3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEaL3ih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEaL3ih.jpg&h=e43244f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方channel宣傳片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SsmsWhGIjx8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSsmsWhGIjx8&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=e9376012\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SsmsWhGIjx8</a><br />\n<br />\n技能展示：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FEgCTt6DvgM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFEgCTt6DvgM&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=312319ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FEgCTt6DvgM</a><br />\n<br />\n5月22有第2次 alpha test:<br />\n<br />\nWe are excited to announce we are holding the 2nd round of alpha testing of Mad World MMO next week on May 22nd. You can head to the Mad World MMO Alpha 01 sign up form for a chance to participate.  ( Alpha 01 is PC only )<br />\n<a href=\"https://register.madworldmmo.com/alpha/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fregister.madworldmmo.com%2Falpha%2F&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=a59895ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://register.madworldmmo.com/alpha/</a><br />\n<br />\nEdit:  To the previous alpha test participants, please apply again to participate the 2nd alpha test.  Apologies for the inconvenience."},{"pid":"d2b807670e60194f92ca78ed4326c056659085c1","tid":1155761,"uid":103879,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"2019年啦<br />\n咁既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011153af9a4898ad40ab1a5d935de00f4412f483","tid":1155761,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"時光機？"},{"pid":"78d7970097ccd6aba5d8207f5b210264938bf078","tid":1155761,"uid":18238,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"上面班友做乜 2019就唔出得2d game 定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344d271588d19adfca4cfbf4e5938fc8243f729e","tid":1155761,"uid":48791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78d7970097ccd6aba5d8207f5b210264938bf078","tid":1155761,"uid":18238,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"上面班友做乜 2019就唔出得2d game 定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b407ec52b308c0279be564504daebcfa0133ec7","tid":1155761,"uid":18238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344d271588d19adfca4cfbf4e5938fc8243f729e","tid":1155761,"uid":48791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78d7970097ccd6aba5d8207f5b210264938bf078","tid":1155761,"uid":18238,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"上面班友做乜 2019就唔出得2d game 定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:38:11.000Z","